# Ignore heavy run outputs (activation caches, tensors), but keep the small,
# explicitly-committed artifacts: manifests, plots, and per-context summaries.
# NOTE: `!*/` is required so git descends into the run subdirectories — without it the
# file re-includes below are silently ignored (a file cannot be re-included if its
# parent directory is excluded by `*`).
*
!*/
!.gitignore
!**/manifest.json
!**/*.png
!**/summary*.json
!**/fourier_*.json
